          class="text-text-body text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-xl mb-4 sm:mb-5 lg:mb-6"
        >
          Bhakti Prema Swami is a Gaudiya Vaishnava sannyasi in the
          International Society for Krishna Consciousness. He is a disciple of
          His Holiness Bhakti Charu Swami, who is a disciple of His Divine Grace
          A.C. Bhaktivedanta Swami Prabhupada, the Founder-Acharya of ISKCON.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-2 sm:mt-3 lg:mt-4">
          <a
            href="/bhakti-prema-swami"
            class="inline-block bg-primary hover:bg-primary-hover text-white px-6 sm:px-7 lg:px-8 py-2.5 sm:py-3 rounded-full text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg transition"
